<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification">
The entity <b>product_identification</b> identifies a manufacturable product in a 
<express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_class"/>.
It is a subtype of 
<express_ref linkend="configuration_management_schema:ir_express:configuration_management_schema.configuration_item"/>
and of 
<express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.characterized_object"/>.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  Attribute: item_concept 
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification.item_concept"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification.item_concept">
The attribute <b>item_concept</b> inherited from the supertype <express_ref linkend="configuration_management_schema:ir_express:configuration_management_schema.configuration_item"/>
references through 
<express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept"/>
the 
<express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_class"/>
of the manufacturable product.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  Where: WR1 
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR1">
Each <b>product_identification</b> shall be referenced as the configuration by 
at most one instance of <b>configuration_design</b> that references as design a 
<express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation"/>
which references as of_product a product which is contained in the of products set of a <b>product_related_product_category</b> with a name of either 'part', 'raw material', or 'tool'
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_identification  Where: WR2 
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR2"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_identification.wr:WR2">
If a <b>product_identification</b> is of type <express_ref linkend="configuration_management_schema:ir_express:configuration_management_schema.configurable_item"/>
it shall also be of type <b>product_specification</b>. 
If a <b>product_identification</b> is of type <b>product_specification</b> 
it shall also be of type <express_ref linkend="configuration_management_schema:ir_express:configuration_management_schema.configurable_item"/>. 
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Specified_product_mim  Entity: product_specification  
   <express_ref linkend="specified_product:mim:Specified_product_mim.product_specification"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Specified_product_mim.product_specification">
The entity <b>product_specification</b>  is a subtype of <b>product_identification</b> and 
<express_ref linkend="configuration_management_schema:ir_express:configuration_management_schema.configurable_item"/>.<p></p>
The inherited attribute item_concept_feature points to a set of 
<express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature_association"/> instances that define the specified characteristics of the manufacturable product.
</ext_description>
